import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import App from "./components/App"
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom"
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"

ReactDOM.render(
  <BrowserRouter>
  <React.StrictMode>
      <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
  </BrowserRouter>,
  document.getElementById("root")
)
